high_descs:
Turn around turn right go straight to the dresser 
Take the mug from the dining table
Turn left go straight turn right to the sink
Put the mug in the clean it and take it back
Turn right go straight walk to the dresser 
Place the mug on the dresser
anns.task_desc: Place the mug on the dresser

high_descs: Turn around to the left, move forward, and turn right. Move forward by turning left, then turn right, then turn left and move forward to the dresser.
Take a mug from the table.
Turn around to the right, move forward, and turn left. Move forward by turning right, then left, then right, then left, then right, then left, and finally turn right and turn left in the sink.
Put the mug in the sink and tap the water to clean it.
Take a cup out of the sink, turn left, move forward, and turn left again. Move forward and turn right, then turn left, then move forward and turn right again, and move forward to the dresser.
Place the mug, top left corner on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Take a mug from the dresser, clean it, and place it in the top left corner of the dresser.

high_descs: walk along to reach the dresser
Take the mug in the table.
Put the mug in the sink, clean it off.
Take back the coffee cup in the dresser.
Place the mug on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Take the mug from the dresser, clean the mug, and place it back on the dresser.
